<section class="section" id="questionnaire">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">What We Actually Ask</span>
      <h2>A peek at the questionnaire.</h2>
      <p class="lede" style="margin-inline:auto;">
        Every Write and Special Request project starts here. Nothing complicated — just
        thoughtful questions that help us listen carefully before a single word is written.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire" open>
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>Tell us your story.</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">How did this chapter begin? We're listening for the details only you would think to include.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>What moment changed everything?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">A turning point, a realization, a decision — the moment the rest of the story turns around.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>Describe this person in three words.</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">Not the words on a greeting card — the words their close friends would actually use.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>What's your favorite memory together?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">Small and ordinary is often better than big and dramatic. We're looking for what's true.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>Any inside jokes we should know about?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">The kind of detail that makes the people who know you best laugh — or tear up — in recognition.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>What qualities do you admire most in them?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">Specific beats general. "Patient" is fine; "the way they explain things twice without sighing" is better.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>How emotional should this feel?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">A simple scale from composed to unabashedly sentimental — so the tone matches what you actually want to feel like reading it.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>How much humor, if any?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">Some people want the room laughing before they get serious. Others don't want a single joke. Both are welcome.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>Is there anything that absolutely must be included?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">A name, a reference, a specific promise — tell us what can't be left out, and we'll build around it.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="questionnaire-card" name="questionnaire">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger"><span>Is there anything you'd rather we avoid?</span>{{ plus() }}</summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">Certain topics, certain phrases, certain relatives. Just as important as what to include.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Process</span>
      <h2>Quiet, careful, and entirely yours.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-step reveal">
        <h4>Share your story</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">A short questionnaire or a conversation — however you'd rather tell it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h4>We listen carefully</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We read between the lines for the details that actually matter to you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h4>We thoughtfully write</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">A first draft, written to sound like you on your most articulate day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal">
        <h4>You review</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">Read it aloud. Sit with it. Tell us what feels off, if anything does.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h4>Together we refine</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We adjust tone, trim length, and sharpen the moments that matter most.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h4>You confidently speak</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">The words are ready. So are you. The moment is entirely yours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

